Hey guys,today i bulit the SLS upper Stage in Ksp. This can be attach to spacecrafts. It got a SAS Module too and a fuel line and it can go to the moon too.

(need KW rocketry and KSPX Expansion pack)

Spaceport Download:

http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/sls-upper-stage/

backup download:

https://www.dropbox.com/s/68efn2d5o5ozn9p/KLS%20Upper%20Stage.zip

Edited July 13, 2013 by ouion
You mean too not two dont you?
So you're one of those guys uploading crappy stuff on the Spaceport, aren't you?
no,i just want to share my rockets and i don't upload crappy stuff you guys.
what's wrong with you guys anyway!? spaceport is not all about mods its about every thing in ksp community

I think he got the wrong person...

Also, don't tag .crafts with anything other than Crafts.

Spaceport is not all about mods, its about every thing in ksp community

No. The Spaceport is made for mods, but the web devs had to add the "craft" category because people kept uploading witty mun landers tagging them with every single tag they could find.
i got updated it and more sls coming soon

what's wrong with you guys anyway!? spaceport is not all about mods its about every thing in ksp community

People would be a lot less upset with you if you had tagged it with CRAFT only, There is no reason for the SAS, RCS, FUEL TANK and LIQUID ENGINE tags.

It really causes problems when people are using the tags to search for new engines.
